title: BelowDeckMed:  Provision Quest
description:
Chef Tom continues to endure endless humiliations: first he has to slice a cucumber — a cucumber!! — and on this week's Below Deck Mediterranean, he also must contend with bad fish and burnt buns. HE'S OVER IT, BLOKE!!!!

Our Patreon Extras: https://patreon.com/watchwhatcrappens
